casebody.data:
BRANDON et al. v. THOMASVILLE REAL ESTATE & IMPROVEMENT CO. et al. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. November 25, 1902.) No. 1,195. Petition to Revise Proceedings in the District Court of the United States for the Southern District of Georgia, in Bankruptcy. John R. L. Smith and W. C. Snodgrass, for petitioners. Washington Dessau and Jos. Hansell Merrill, for respondents.

Before PARDEE, McCORMICK, and SHELBY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The petition for review herein is denied.
